  Created by MyDrift (https://github.com/mydrift-user/ngx-dwex)
  ```

- **In compiled applications**: Include a visible credit in the application's UI (e.g., in an "About" section, footer, or settings):
  ```
  Built with Dwex by MyDrift
  ```

- **In public repositories**: Add the following to your README.md:
  ```
  This project is based on [Dwex](https://github.com/mydrift-user/ngx-dwex) by [MyDrift](https://github.com/mydrift-user)
  ```

- **In documentation**: If you create documentation, mention that the Shell is based on Dwex.

### 2. Citation Requirement
When referencing this Shell in academic work, presentations, or technical documentation, you MUST cite:

```
Dwex - A Modern Angular Shell
Author: MyDrift
Repository: https://github.com/mydrift-user/ngx-dwex
```

